# Controlled query-arg signature list for the Phase 6 protocol/decode harness
# (tests/run-protocol-tests.sh). NOT a production list -- the patterns are
# chosen so each percent-decode edge case in ngx_http_heavybag_sig_lookup_decoded
# (module.c:856) + ngx_unescape_uri(type=0) (module.c:873) maps to an unambiguous
# (status,reason) verdict. r->args is %-decoded EXACTLY ONCE, then matched
# case-insensitively (the single-pass contract, match-01).
#
# Two patterns, two distinct actions, so a hit's action proves WHICH pattern
# fired (no first-match ambiguity across the file):
#   union   -> 403   (a bare substring: isolates the DECODE transform)
#   'union  -> 404   (literal apostrophe prefix: isolates SINGLE-PASS decode --
#                     a double-encoded %2527union decodes once to "%27union",
#                     which lacks the literal quote and must NOT match)
union    403
'union   404
